    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-06-25T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-06-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="368"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d368">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Dupuy de Lôme</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Spain</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-06-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 25, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary</hi>: I have had the honor to receive your
                    excellency’s notes of the 22d and 21th instant relative to the Mora claim.</p>
                <p>I immediately communicated a résumé of said notes by cable to the Government of
                    His Majesty the King, my august sovereign, and in reply I have received
                    instructions to inform you that the Spanish Government, which is as desirous as
                    is that of the United States to avoid any cause of unpleasantness between two
                    friendly nations, will answer as soon as it receives the text, which I have
                    already forwarded by mail, furnishing the satisfactory solution that is desired
                    by both Governments.</p>
                <p>I avail myself, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Enrique Dupuy de Lôme</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
